summary: A test suite that validates TensorFlow GPT-2 model implementations, covering configuration, various model heads, attention masking, past-key handling, large input processing, sequence classification, loading from pretrained checkpoints, and ONNX export compliance and optimization.
business_intent: Guarantee the correctness, stability and deployment readiness of GPT-2 models in TensorFlow environments, supporting reliable integration and performance tuning for production AI applications.
